nodes.text: Jedi Artisan Contest is an article written by Morrie Mullins as a tie in to the Living Force campaign. It was published on the Wizards of the Coast website on May 13, 2003 and provided players the opportunity to apply to be made one of only five Jedi artisan apprentices taken by Felanil Baaks. It would require players to sit out a month of gameplay in the Living Force campaign.
